import React from 'react';
import { Menu, Segment, Sidebar, Icon } from 'semantic-ui-react';

const Sidenav = () => {
  return (
    <Sidebar.Pushable as={Segment}>
    <Sidebar
      as={Menu}
      animation='overlay'
      icon='labeled'
      inverted
      vertical
      visible
      width='thin'
    >
        <Menu.Item as='a'>
          <Icon name='home' />
          Home
        </Menu.Item>
        <Menu.Item as='a'>
          <Icon name='gamepad' />
          Games
        </Menu.Item>
        <Menu.Item as='a'>
          <Icon name='camera' />
          Channels
        </Menu.Item>
      </Sidebar>
    </Sidebar.Pushable>
  )
  
}

export default Sidenav;
